<p><strong><em>Magic Weapons.</em></strong> The ki-rinâ€™s weapon attacks are magical.</p>

<p><strong><em>Spellcasting.</em></strong> The ki-rin is a 18th-level spellcaster. Its spellcasting ability is Wisdom (spell save DC 17, +9 to hit with spell attacks). It has the following cleric spells prepared:</p>

